%N A076453 a(n+2) = abs(a(n+1)) - a(n), a(0)=1, a(1)=0.
%C A076453 For any initial values a(0), a(1), the sequence of real numbers {a(n)} satisfying the relation a(n+2) = |a(n+1)| - a(n) is periodic with period 9.
